public class ClinicalStatement
extends Phrase
A kind of Named Entity that contains a clinical statement. Clinical statements are the atomic level labeled components of a section or document within a CDA document. Clinical Statements typically identify a label from a controlled medical vocabulary via the coded Entries slots.
